quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,Rivalry in worldly increase distracts you (from the remembrance of God)
  102,2,till you come to the graves
  102,3,"No, you will know"
  102,4,"Again, no, you will know"
  102,5,"No, if you know (having) the knowledge that is certain"
  102,6,you will definitely see hell fire
  102,7,Then you will definitely see it with the eye of certainty
  102,8,Then on that day you will definitely be questioned about the comforts